body:
What does `echo | /opt/rh/devtoolset-2/root/usr/bin/gcc -E -xc++ - -v` says?

It seems like your compiler doesn't like your own installation. Can you try to restore /usr/bin/gcc and /usr/bin/g++ to the default value?
